00:24:25.142 --> 00:24:28.822
I must say, he speaks
well; the way he turns phrases

00:24:29.182 --> 00:24:31.222
He was good at debate in college

00:24:32.422 --> 00:24:38.182
'Her smile sends ripples of delight'

00:24:38.942 --> 00:24:41.102
The boys in saffron
made a pretty picture

00:24:46.942 --> 00:24:51.343
That makes the Love-God swoon

00:24:56.023 --> 00:24:57.182
How long will he stay ?

00:24:58.663 --> 00:25:00.302
He'll go to Rongpur tomorrow

00:25:03.103 --> 00:25:05.263
He'll work from there

00:25:06.801 --> 00:25:08.302
Do you want to meet him ?

00:25:10.044 --> 00:25:12.964
What's the use ?
I'll have nothing to say

00:25:14.044 --> 00:25:17.604
