00:28:12.313 --> 00:28:17.033
At first I couldn't believe my eyes

00:28:19.033 --> 00:28:21.153
Now I can't believe my ears

00:28:21.993 --> 00:28:23.873
My husband is exaggerating

00:28:24.913 --> 00:28:28.513
