I'll be more than happy

00:28:29.873 --> 00:28:31.873
Whatever I may
accomplish as a politician ...

00:28:32.396 --> 00:28:35.596
... you have already
achieved a social revolution

00:28:36.476 --> 00:28:39.996
And I know what that means

00:28:40.076 --> 00:28:45.076
I also realize that you're
no mere shadow of your husband

00:28:45.418 --> 00:28:47.116
You have a mind of you own

00:28:48.676 --> 00:28:52.276
