00:28:52.716 --> 00:28:55.596
Go on like that and
she'll be walking on air

00:28:55.676 --> 00:28:57.756
You can't stop me

00:28:58.636 --> 00:29:02.396
As a politician I'm brazen
about seeking support for my cause

00:29:04.116 --> 00:29:06.956
I haven't yet succeeded
in persuading a woman ...

00:29:07.836 --> 00:29:14.436
... but should that ever happen,
I'd be delighted

00:29:16.116 --> 00:29:22.756
Women have this rare
quality of intuition

00:29:24.316 --> 00:29:26.196
I admire it greatly

00:29:27.236 --> 00:29:30.436
Man's powers of reasoning pale beside it

00:29:31.876 --> 00:29:33.076
What do you say, Nikhil ?

00:29:35.556 --> 00:29:38.836
Tell him what you thought of his speech

00:29:39.156 --> 00:29:40.196
Oh yes.

00:29:41.436 --> 00:29:43.476
I was going to ask you

00:29:44.837 --> 00:29:45.676
Tell me.

00:29:48.356 --> 00:29:51.076
Did it sound like drivel to you ?

00:29:52.476 --> 00:29:53.916
Come on, don't hesitate

00:29:55.076 --> 00:29:56.996
I haven't had much time to think

00:29:57.076 --> 00:29:58.956
That's precisely why I'm asking you

00:29:59.556 --> 00:30:03.996
Thinking is for him; you tell
me what comes from your heart

00:30:04.396 --> 00:30:05.796
Forget about making
sense when you speak.

00:30:07.876 --> 00:30:12.920
I fell that if the British have
done wrong to split up Bengal ...

00:30:12.996 --> 00:30:18.396
... then we should not let it pass

00:30:19.625 --> 00:30:23.756
If Swadeshi can shake them
a bit, then we should do it

00:30:23.836 --> 00:30:25.756
Yes, yes.

00:30:27.056 --> 00:30:30.716
Of course, it won't help if only
a few people take up the cause

00:30:31.567 --> 00:30:36.356
But if the whole country wakes
up to it, then we may succeed

00:30:36.860 --> 00:30:37.860
Absolutely.

00:30:39.180 --> 00:30:42.380
Bravo ! That is exactly what we aim at

00:30:43.420 --> 00:30:46.700
That is what our battle-cry
is for : Hail Motherland !

00:30:47.460 --> 00:30:50.700
Awaken the nation. Isn't
there magic in those two words ?

00:30:51.220 --> 00:30:53.140
Have you tried them ?

00:30:56.180 --> 00:30:57.460
Please do.

00:30:58.380 --> 00:31:00.863
You need not raise
your voice; softly will do

00:31:00.940 --> 00:31:05.700
As a matter of fact, when
all of you gave that cry,

00:31:06.321 --> 00:31:07.620
I felt a ...

00:31:08.220 --> 00:31:09.380
Thrill ?

00:31:11.460 --> 00:31:12.900
A shiver down the spine

00:31:13.020 --> 00:31:14.340
That's as it should be

00:31:15.420 --> 00:31:19.180
