around here to help the cause

00:35:44.856 --> 00:35:47.556
Why not leave my estate alone?

00:35:47.916 --> 00:35:52.596
You see, not a shred
of patriotism in him!

00:35:57.156 --> 00:35:58.196
Anyway.

00:35:59.876 --> 00:36:00.677
So tell me.

00:36:03.097 --> 00:36:04.556
Are you joining our party or not?

00:36:05.717 --> 00:36:09.036
Don't worry, you don't have
to sign a pledge or anything

00:36:10.166 --> 00:36:12.077
You'll stay exactly as you are

00:36:12.740 --> 00:36:14.837
I'll come to you in case of need

00:36:16.196 --> 00:36:16.997
What is it? Tell me.

00:36:17.996 --> 00:36:20.357
Well? Yes or no?

00:36:22.116 --> 00:36:23.036
All right

00:36:23.316 --> 00:36:24.036
Good.

00:36:24.437 --> 00:36:25.517
