00:38:13.196 --> 00:38:15.317
What you thought of my friend

00:38:15.846 --> 00:38:18.677
But we've only met once

00:38:19.915 --> 00:38:21.396
I think the less one knows

00:38:22.435 --> 00:38:24.996
Sandip, the better one likes him

00:38:25.915 --> 00:38:28.435
You seem to have so little in common;

00:38:29.155 --> 00:38:32.035
I wonder how you ever became friends

00:38:34.836 --> 00:38:36.595
That's not unusual, Bimala

00:38:38.596 --> 00:38:42.436
Friendships are not
worked out mathematically

00:38:44.431 --> 00:38:47.356
We've been friends since college

00:38:49.036 --> 00:38:51.036
It's not that we had nothing in common

00:38:52.795 --> 00:38:59.236
We both decided to have nothing
to do with irrational conventions

00:39:00.396 --> 00:39:04.476
He was even more radical than I

00:39:07.036 --> 00:39:09.115
When his parents
arranged a bride for him...

00:39:10.075 --> 00:39:13.756
...he was so annoyed he
severed all ties with them

00:39:19.836 --> 00:39:23.916
Soon after we were married he
asked to be introduced to you

00:39:26.515 --> 00:39:29.196
He would remind me from time to time

00:39:31.671 --> 00:39:33.198
Finally he said:

00:39:33.876 --> 00:39:37.116
" I don't word of what
you say about your wife"

00:39:43.490 --> 00:39:45.076
And do you know what he said today

00:39:45.196 --> 00:39:45.796
What?

00:39:52.795 --> 00:39:55.036
I shall not tell you
- Why not?

00:39:57.940 --> 00:40:00.115
What can he say after
such a brief meeting?

00:40:01.506 --> 00:40:03.876
I can say a lot more

00:40:05.179 --> 00:40:06.756
But you never do

00:40:08.977 --> 00:40:14.137
Do I have to? Don't
you have your intuition?

00:40:53.776 --> 00:40:55.057
Madam

00:40:55.537 --> 00:40:56.536
What is it?

00:40:56.656 --> 00:40:58.696
A letter from Mr. Mukherji

00:41:07.777 --> 00:41:12.736
I hope the rule was
not broken for just a day

00:41:12.976 --> 00:41:15.777
Can I see you for a moment?

00:41:16.617 --> 00:41:18.097
Tell him I'm coming

00:41:18.177 --> 00:41:19.177
Okay.

00:41:23.457 --> 00:41:27.376
When Krishna's flute
beckons so, I must go

