of your many accomplishments

00:43:28.536 --> 00:43:31.500
You've learnt English from a memsahib

00:43:31.576 --> 00:43:34.976
You love books, needlework, cooking

00:43:35.492 --> 00:43:41.176
I even know your favourite dishes,
what flowers you like...

00:43:43.653 --> 00:43:45.416
I also know something else

00:43:47.176 --> 00:43:49.536
You resent the fact...

00:43:49.776 --> 00:43:51.816
...that I borrow money from Nikhil

00:43:53.416 --> 00:43:55.256
So you really are no stranger to me

00:43:56.336 --> 00:43:59.096
But I never imagined I'd
one day find myself....

00:44:00.520 --> 00:44:04.440
...sitting by your side

00:44:05.659 --> 00:44:08.360
