Hail Motherland !

01:05:42.110 --> 01:05:43.790
Hail Motherland !

01:05:43.870 --> 01:05:45.514
Hail Motherland !

01:05:45.590 --> 01:05:47.310
Hail Motherland !

01:05:47.430 --> 01:05:49.070
Hail Motherland !

01:05:49.150 --> 01:05:50.830
Hail Motherland !

01:05:50.910 --> 01:05:52.393
This is Mr. Sanyal

01:05:52.470 --> 01:05:54.153
Greetings.

01:05:54.229 --> 01:05:55.950
Come on.

01:06:00.682 --> 01:06:03.281
Were those snatched from the villagers ?

01:06:03.682 --> 01:06:04.961
Yes. German wrappers

01:06:10.082 --> 01:06:10.802
Sit down.

01:06:12.289 --> 01:06:16.322
You may enjoy bonfire, but
those fellows may have you up

01:06:18.842 --> 01:06:22.121
We'll set fire to their crops if they do

01:06:23.362 --> 01:06:24.962
Can't we try picketing ?

01:06:26.842 --> 01:06:30.202
It's worked elsewhere

01:06:31.202 --> 01:06:35.321
Picketing won't work here; I
know what works and what doesn't

01:06:37.396 --> 01:06:38.362
Sit down.

01:06:45.682 --> 01:06:47.561
An English brand, I see

01:06:48.482 --> 01:06:50.282
One item where I draw
the line at Swadeshi

01:06:50.678 --> 01:06:51.641
May I try one ?

01:06:51.881 --> 01:06:52.562
Sure.

01:06:56.349 --> 01:06:57.962
These people won't
take persuasion, Amulya

01:06:58.376 --> 01:07:00.002
They've been pampered too much

01:07:00.253 --> 01:07:01.162
Listen.

01:07:01.654 --> 01:07:03.962
I've been Manager of this estate since

01:07:04.209 --> 01:07:07.369
the time of the
present landlord's father

01:07:08.970 --> 01:07:13.288
The father was a tough one;
the trouble is with the son

01:07:13.719 --> 01:07:15.529
If only he'd been firm,

01:07:15.759 --> 01:07:19.089
he could have brought
these fellows to their knees

01:07:19.502 --> 01:07:21.808
It would be plain selling for you

01:07:24.529 --> 01:07:26.968
Tell me how you can help

01:07:28.849 --> 01:07:32.449
If you can't stop the
influx of foreign goods ...

01:07:33.409 --> 01:07:36.409
... you can't stop the trade in them

01:07:37.729 --> 01:07:41.289
Those boats bring in the goods;

01:07:42.609 --> 01:07:45.369
you have to deal with the boatmen first

01:07:45.828 --> 01:07:46.929
Can you do that for me ?

01:07:47.809 --> 01:07:53.169
The trouble is, the
boatmen's leader is a stubborn fellow

01:07:54.946 --> 01:07:57.009
What's his name ?

01:07:57.249 --> 01:08:00.369
Mirjan. A Muslim.
He's a hard nut to crack

01:08:01.908 --> 01:08:02.968
Can't he be brought round ?

01:08:03.529 --> 01:08:05.169
There's a way round everything,
Mr. Mukerji

01:08:06.328 --> 01:08:12.169
A boat which sails is
also a boat which sinks

01:08:15.208 --> 01:08:18.688
But this is where you
need more than words

01:08:19.932 --> 01:08:20.972
You need ...

01:08:21.532 --> 01:08:22.372
Money ?

01:08:23.012 --> 01:08:26.692
We have to stop tongues wagging,
pay compensation ...

01:08:26.932 --> 01:08:30.252
... bribe the police
- it all needs hard cash

01:08:33.892 --> 01:08:39.612
It's not that we haven't money
- and more can be raised

01:08:39.852 --> 01:08:42.052
Then you can rely on me

01:08:43.572 --> 01:08:47.132
I'll do the dirty work all right ...

01:08:47.532 --> 01:08:50.572
... but if it proves awkward for you,

01:08:51.012 --> 01:08:52.452
..you'll have to fend for yourself

01:08:55.345 --> 01:08:57.412
You need not worry about that.

01:08:57.878 --> 01:09:00.332
But if I find myself in trouble ...

01:09:00.612 --> 01:09:02.772
... I'm not taking all the blame

01:09:11.012 --> 01:09:12.852
I mean to preserve this letter from you

01:09:16.732 --> 01:09:20.292
I didn't go. He asked for me

01:09:20.692 --> 01:09:25.252
I gave an excuse and stayed back,
but what good did it do ?

01:09:25.732 --> 01:09:29.172
All day yesterday I kept thinking of him

01:09:29.652 --> 01:09:32.252
Why should this happen to a woman who

01:09:32.332 --> 01:09:35.892
never had a thought of any man ...

01:09:36.437 --> 01:09:38.052
... except her own husband ?

01:09:38.920 --> 01:09:42.972
You didn't say you
wanted the fish cooked, madam

01:09:44.528 --> 01:09:46.292
Make curry with ground mustard-seed

01:09:55.190 --> 01:09:56.351
Younger madam.

01:09:58.190 --> 01:09:58.910
Yes, Nanku ?

01:09:59.671 --> 01:10:01.351
A letter for you

01:10:10.751 --> 01:10:11.831
Are you better ?

01:10:14.431 --> 01:10:15.191
Yes, thank you

01:10:16.031 --> 01:10:19.190
This boy from our group
is very keen to meet you

01:10:22.831 --> 01:10:27.071
You've seen me once when I was
little; I came with my mother

01:10:27.590 --> 01:10:29.831
What is your mother's name ?
- Soudamini Devi

01:10:30.830 --> 01:10:32.992
You're Nibaron Ghosal's son ?

01:10:33.069 --> 01:10:35.471
Yes. My name is Amulya

01:10:37.311 --> 01:10:38.630
How old are you ?

01:10:39.191 --> 01:10:42.470
Seventeen. I was about to
sit my final exam, but I didn't

01:10:43.088 --> 01:10:44.311
Because of Swadeshi ?

01:10:45.151 --> 01:10:46.751
Amulya is a good worker

01:10:47.870 --> 01:10:49.151
He knows the Gita

01:10:50.630 --> 01:10:51.511
Really?

01:10:53.270 --> 01:10:53.831
Here it is.

01:10:54.709 --> 01:10:56.311
Do you always carry it ?

01:10:56.390 --> 01:11:01.111
Always. The Gita gives one courage

01:11:01.310 --> 01:11:03.311
Even to die for one's country

01:11:05.711 --> 01:11:07.070
Aren't you afraid to die ?

01:11:08.191 --> 01:11:13.910
Even when a man dies, his soul lives

01:11:14.212 --> 01:11:17.030
It always remains constant.

01:11:17.270 --> 01:11:19.831
Soul doesn't get destroyed.
Only the body does.

01:11:20.311 --> 01:11:22.231
Even if a man dies,
soul never dies, sister.

01:11:22.711 --> 01:11:24.991
You may go now

01:11:27.031 --> 01:11:31.351
Mr. Mukerji said you believed in
Swadeshi. I wanted to pay my respects

01:11:31.751 --> 01:11:32.591
I am leaving, sister.

01:11:34.031 --> 01:11:36.110
I'll come again.
- Please do

01:11:36.555 --> 01:11:37.790
Hail Motherland !

01:11:39.071 --> 01:11:39.881
Hail Motherland !

01:11:39.958 --> 01:11:40.471
I am leaving.

01:11:52.151 --> 01:11:53.510
What are you thinking ?

01:11:54.671 --> 01:11:57.551
Is there any danger to
your life in the work you do ?

01:12:04.350 --> 01:12:08.150
Since we set ourselves
against our formidable rulers ...

01:12:10.231 --> 01:12:11.951
... there certainly is

01:12:18.195 --> 01:12:21.110
But my boys are a plucky lot

01:12:22.790 --> 01:12:24.230
My courage doesn't match theirs

01:12:24.513 --> 01:12:27.311
That's a strange
confession from a leader

01:12:30.216 --> 01:12:32.096
Sometimes the truth comes out

01:12:37.256 --> 01:12:39.296
Now may I have a bit of truth from you ?

01:12:40.656 --> 01:12:41.175
What ?

01:12:43.136 --> 01:12:47.535
After so many years, why suddenly
decide to come out of seclusion ?

01:12:48.735 --> 01:12:50.336
Don't you know why ?

01:12:51.252 --> 01:12:52.376
How should I know ?

01:12:53.117 --> 01:12:59.496
You ought to know, you're a man

01:12:59.959 --> 01:13:01.935
But you haven't a woman's intuition

01:13:03.731 --> 01:13:05.376
Will you tell me why ?

01:13:31.171 --> 01:13:34.051
I'd never been face to
face with a leader before

01:13:36.491 --> 01:13:40.291
I fear the leader may have let you down

01:13:48.011 --> 01:13:49.771
Not so far

01:14:13.451 --> 01:14:15.051
You play the piano, too ?

01:14:16.371 --> 01:14:21.731
I was taking lessons.
Piano ... singing ...

01:14:23.371 --> 01:14:24.251
English songs ?

01:14:27.388 --> 01:14:32.731
"That to me were so dear."

01:14:33.291 --> 01:14:39.451
"Long, long ago. Long, long ago."

01:14:41.801 --> 01:14:44.091
"Same are the songs."

01:14:44.290 --> 01:14:47.971
"I am delighted to hear."

01:14:48.511 --> 01:14:51.091
"Long, long ago. Long, long ago."

01:14:52.398 --> 01:14:54.731
"Long ago."

01:14:56.206 --> 01:14:57.331
Yesterday ...

01:14:58.371 --> 01:15:02.571
... I had a feeling that
you were not really well

01:15:03.927 --> 01:15:06.291
I racked my brains
all day trying to guess

01:15:07.491 --> 01:15:13.211
What had I done or said to annoy you ?

01:15:16.331 --> 01:15:19.331
You haven't told me yet why you called

01:15:20.171 --> 01:15:21.811
I just wanted to see you

01:15:23.889 --> 01:15:25.211
Is that the reason ?

01:15:28.571 --> 01:15:32.531
I didn't see you yesterday and it
turned out to be a dismal day for me

01:15:33.691 --> 01:15:38.331
My pride as a leader was badly shaken

01:15:39.291 --> 01:15:40.971
The people won't listen to you ?

01:15:41.771 --> 01:15:44.571
Sometimes words are not enough

01:15:45.091 --> 01:15:48.291
Why do you do then ?
- Try other ways

01:15:49.731 --> 01:15:51.171
May I know what ways ?

01:15:52.398 --> 01:15:54.851
Because my husband's
not going to help you

01:15:59.142 --> 01:16:00.331
Has Nikhil said so ?

01:16:08.684 --> 01:16:10.685
Do you know what I feel sometimes ?

01:16:11.525 --> 01:16:12.845
To hell with Swadeshi !

01:16:13.925 --> 01:16:16.604
I'll spend my life chatting to Queen Bee

01:16:18.524 --> 01:16:21.404
With me ?... You ?

01:16:22.565 --> 01:16:23.645
Would you mind ?

01:16:27.365 --> 01:16:28.644
Why laugh ?

01:16:29.244 --> 01:16:31.724
It's so absurd

01:16:32.285 --> 01:16:35.804
You're not the type to
spend even an hour chatting

01:16:39.119 --> 01:16:40.205
You're right

01:16:42.125 --> 01:16:43.284
The truth is ...

01:16:44.645 --> 01:16:48.764
... I need politics
as much as I need you

01:16:52.205 --> 01:16:54.804
I don't want you to give up at all

01:16:56.242 --> 01:16:59.964
My husband and I don't
see eye to eye on this

01:17:00.884 --> 01:17:04.685
He has many gifts and
I admire him for them

01:17:05.964 --> 01:17:11.165
But he is much too placid

01:17:11.924 --> 01:17:14.964
You can't afford to be
so at a time like this

01:17:18.564 --> 01:17:20.364
I entirely agree with you

01:17:22.738 --> 01:17:26.004
My husband says you
don't think of poor ...

01:17:26.800 --> 01:17:29.124
... so you can't really
do the country any good

01:17:32.804 --> 01:17:36.044
I don't believe you'll hurt the poor

01:17:36.924 --> 01:17:40.044
You'll do as much as
possible with persuasion

01:17:46.205 --> 01:17:47.684
But the problem is ...

01:17:50.285 --> 01:17:52.445
... persuasion doesn't always work

01:17:54.686 --> 01:17:57.845
You need more than that.
- What do you need ?

01:18:01.404 --> 01:18:04.205
Let's not talk about that.
- I want to know

01:18:05.784 --> 01:18:08.246
I don't want to talk about
mundane matters with you

01:18:08.323 --> 01:18:09.164
Why?

01:18:12.019 --> 01:18:15.219
I want no note of
discord in our relationship

01:18:16.012 --> 01:18:18.499
But I'd be really happy to help

01:18:20.100 --> 01:18:21.459
This is beyond you, Queen

01:18:22.380 --> 01:18:24.660
Haven't you seen me
going beyond myself ?

01:18:25.649 --> 01:18:27.699
I know you can go a long way.

01:18:27.776 --> 01:18:30.900
Even so, I'd rather not talk about it

01:18:32.739 --> 01:18:37.380
Then there's no reason for me to stay

01:18:38.419 --> 01:18:39.139
I am leaving.

01:18:39.900 --> 01:18:43.500
Please, don't go away like that

01:18:43.740 --> 01:18:48.103
If I'm not needed for the cause,
then I'm just wasting my time here

01:18:48.180 --> 01:18:50.619
I didn't wish to cause
you anxiety for my sake

01:18:51.180 --> 01:18:55.339
Is politics, my work, the
only thing we must talk about ?

01:18:55.860 --> 01:18:59.139
Promise you'll tell
me if you need money,

01:18:59.304 --> 01:19:01.316
..and you'll take it if I give it

01:19:01.393 --> 01:19:02.063
I promise

01:19:02.775 --> 01:19:07.459
I will give my word,
Mukhi. I am giving my word.

01:19:08.820 --> 01:19:11.460
I'll come again this evening.
Please wait for me here

01:19:12.060 --> 01:19:14.379
I hate having to send for you every time

01:19:14.940 --> 01:19:16.099
Let go of me

01:19:16.548 --> 01:19:20.619
Promise that you'll come to me everyday

01:19:21.420 --> 01:19:24.099
I must see you at least once every day

01:19:25.380 --> 01:19:29.539
There's nothing
wrong in that. Promise me

01:19:30.180 --> 01:19:31.339
All right

01:19:33.599 --> 01:19:36.900
Please let go of my hand. I want to go

01:20:00.259 --> 01:20:02.619
Khemi, do the room later

01:21:15.168 --> 01:21:20.340
Gently she walks, the Beauteous One

01:21:26.816 --> 01:21:28.539
Back so early ?

01:21:32.940 --> 01:21:34.260
What are you gawping at ?

01:21:36.699 --> 01:21:41.460
What is there to gawp at
but you ? Such goings on !

01:21:43.164 --> 01:21:47.499
Such tender concern for our guest;
enough to make him stay for ever

01:21:49.298 --> 01:21:53.580
In our time we had to
look after our husbands, too

01:21:56.059 --> 01:22:02.139
If only my brother-in-law were a
guest here, he'd be warmly welcomed

01:22:02.384 --> 01:22:04.939
I don't want any advice from you

01:22:10.500 --> 01:22:13.020
I was a small girl when
I came here as a bride

01:22:14.203 --> 01:22:18.259
Your husband was my playmate then

01:22:20.460 --> 01:22:21.780
Where were you then ?

01:22:22.166 --> 01:22:24.900
You need not repeat what I already know

01:22:30.046 --> 01:22:31.637
He was the only one who felt for me

01:22:32.481 --> 01:22:33.241
He used to say :

01:22:34.634 --> 01:22:39.459
" We're still in the Dark Ages,
that's why you suffer so "

01:22:41.499 --> 01:22:45.060
" For you, having a husband is
just as painful as losing one

01:22:45.708 --> 01:22:50.779
" My wife shall be a
free woman ", he'd say

01:22:53.664 --> 01:22:56.340
Well, I see the free
woman before my eyes

01:23:00.663 --> 01:23:05.019
But don't forget, dear sister,
there is a God above us ...

01:23:06.229 --> 01:23:09.099
... and He has eyes, too

01:23:22.277 --> 01:23:24.117
I believed I had strength to bear ...

01:23:25.236 --> 01:23:29.796
... whatever misfortune
Fate had in store for me

01:23:30.597 --> 01:23:35.517
I would call up visions of
suffering and steel myself against them

01:23:36.717 --> 01:23:41.757
Visions of poverty,
imprisonment, dishonour, death ...

01:23:42.957 --> 01:23:45.837
... even Bimala's death

01:23:47.477 --> 01:23:50.237
But one thing I could
never imagine happening

01:23:51.957 --> 01:23:55.277
Now I keep asking
myself again and again..

01:23:56.574 --> 01:23:58.116
..have I the strength to bear this ?

01:23:58.197 --> 01:23:59.957
Hail Motherland !

01:24:00.036 --> 01:24:02.037
Hail Motherland !

01:24:02.117 --> 01:24:03.917
Hail Motherland !

01:24:03.996 --> 01:24:06.036
Hail Motherland !

01:24:06.117 --> 01:24:07.716
Hail Motherland !

01:24:07.797 --> 01:24:09.756
Hail Motherland !

01:24:09.837 --> 01:24:11.676
Hail Motherland !

01:24:11.757 --> 01:24:13.716
Hail Motherland !

01:24:13.797 --> 01:24:15.557
Hail Motherland !

01:24:15.636 --> 01:24:17.637
Hail Motherland !

01:24:17.717 --> 01:24:19.517
Hail Motherland !

01:24:23.477 --> 01:24:24.437
What do you want ?

01:24:25.077 --> 01:24:27.156
We have some questions

01:24:27.797 --> 01:24:28.557
Hail Motherland !

01:24:29.076 --> 01:24:31.836
Why don't you clear our
market of foreign goods ?

01:24:32.357 --> 01:24:33.437
I have a reason

01:24:33.557 --> 01:24:35.556
You'd lose by it ?

01:24:37.677 --> 01:24:41.397
Not me, but the poor would lose

01:24:42.117 --> 01:24:43.557
The country will gain.

01:24:43.801 --> 01:24:47.357
We've given up foreign
goods for the country's sake

01:24:47.733 --> 01:24:51.756
How can you compare
yourselves with the poor ?

01:24:53.100 --> 01:24:57.516
You can afford to
spend more on Indian goods

01:24:59.418 --> 01:25:03.837
The poor do not stand in your way.
Why do you stand in theirs ?

01:25:04.097 --> 01:25:07.000
You want to oppose a nation
that's taken the vow of Swadeshi ?

01:25:07.077 --> 01:25:09.996
It's beyond my power to do so

01:25:11.293 --> 01:25:14.196
But how can you say the
nation's taken your vow ?

01:25:15.151 --> 01:25:19.150
Aren't the traders part of the nation ?

01:25:19.310 --> 01:25:22.711
So you won't throw out foreign goods ?

01:25:23.990 --> 01:25:27.350
No, because the
goods do not belong to me

01:25:28.297 --> 01:25:30.031
Hail Motherland !

01:25:30.110 --> 01:25:31.990
Hail Motherland !

01:25:32.071 --> 01:25:33.871
Hail Motherland !

01:25:33.950 --> 01:25:35.753
Hail Motherland !

01:25:35.830 --> 01:25:37.634
Hail Motherland !

01:25:37.711 --> 01:25:39.430
Hail Motherland !

01:25:39.507 --> 01:25:41.390
Hail Motherland !

01:25:42.430 --> 01:25:46.990
No, I think this is the one.

01:25:51.271 --> 01:25:52.790
What are you looking for ?

01:25:53.750 --> 01:25:58.270
Passiflora. Didn't you have a phial ?

01:26:00.468 --> 01:26:01.910
Have you been sleeping badly ?

01:26:03.910 --> 01:26:07.111
One sleeps less as one grows older ...

01:26:08.178 --> 01:26:09.909
... but less these last three nights

01:26:11.350 --> 01:26:13.231
Here it is

01:26:13.951 --> 01:26:15.151
Please keep the phial

01:26:16.071 --> 01:26:16.910
Thank you.

01:26:25.724 --> 01:26:27.790
I don't like it, Nikhil

01:26:29.298 --> 01:26:35.110
I have grave misgivings
about the way things are shaping

01:26:36.390 --> 01:26:42.710
Everyone knows that Sandip
is your friend and your guest

01:26:43.475 --> 01:26:47.390
Soon they'll believe that
whatever he's doing has your sanction

01:26:48.477 --> 01:26:53.230
Don't you realise the terrible
consequences it may have for you ?

01:26:55.589 --> 01:26:58.030
The consequences can
already be felt, sir

01:26:59.148 --> 01:27:00.871
That I'm a lackey of the British ...

01:27:01.787 --> 01:27:04.111
... that I don't force Swadeshi

01:27:04.190 --> 01:27:07.302
.. on my tenants for
fear they'd stop paying rent

01:27:07.379 --> 01:27:08.202
No, no.

01:27:08.279 --> 01:27:09.991
Don't let that worry you

01:27:10.567 --> 01:27:15.470
Nothing can touch you as long
as you have a clear conscience

01:27:16.498 --> 01:27:19.510
But the portents are bad, Nikhil

01:27:21.486 --> 01:27:26.990
Muslim preachers from Dacca are
going around setting on the peasants

01:27:27.430 --> 01:27:28.630
Do you keep a check on those?

01:27:30.031 --> 01:27:31.777
I've read about it in the papers

01:27:31.911 --> 01:27:34.231
What's to stop them coming here ?

01:27:35.562 --> 01:27:36.604
Nothing

01:27:36.681 --> 01:27:37.510
So?

01:27:40.113 --> 01:27:41.512
If anything should happen,

01:27:42.832 --> 01:27:46.353
..how could we put all the
blame on the preachers ?

01:27:47.752 --> 01:27:51.793
What about our own responsibility ?

01:27:53.992 --> 01:27:56.673
Think how we ourselves
have treated the poor Muslims

01:27:58.095 --> 01:28:01.792
Have we even given them
their dues as human beings ?

01:28:02.232 --> 01:28:05.512
That's true, but what's to be done now ?

01:28:09.226 --> 01:28:10.265
I'll go around

01:28:12.145 --> 01:28:17.305
I'll see for myself. Rumours can mislead

01:28:18.065 --> 01:28:21.305
Can't you have a word
with the Magistrate ?

01:28:22.265 --> 01:28:24.505
I don't think he'd mind a riot;

01:28:25.546 --> 01:28:27.586
that would make short work of Swadeshi

01:28:27.905 --> 01:28:29.945
There is one thing you can do

01:28:32.185 --> 01:28:34.666
You can at least root out
the source of the trouble.

01:28:35.945 --> 01:28:37.825
Why let Sandip stay ?

01:28:45.346 --> 01:28:47.105
I thought he'd leave his own accord

01:28:50.986 --> 01:28:52.505
But now ...

01:28:52.865 --> 01:28:55.666
Leave ? Why ?

01:28:56.305 --> 01:28:59.146
With all the comfort and
protection he enjoys here ?

01:28:59.785 --> 01:29:04.985
Besides, you've done him a special
favour, introducing him to your wife

01:29:05.225 --> 01:29:07.465
Isn't he taking full advantage of that ?

01:29:08.185 --> 01:29:11.266
I'd no idea he'd changed so much

01:29:11.665 --> 01:29:16.906
All this adulation has turned his head

01:29:18.946 --> 01:29:23.345
I think it comes from a
deep sense of frustration

01:29:25.458 --> 01:29:30.865
With all his gifts, he
couldn't really accomplish anything

01:29:32.851 --> 01:29:36.826
Sometimes I feel pity for him

01:29:37.263 --> 01:29:39.865
This is no time for pity, Nikhil

01:29:40.640 --> 01:29:44.866
You can't bring
yourself to be firm with him,

01:29:45.184 --> 01:29:46.666
..because he's close to you ...

01:29:47.401 --> 01:29:51.665
... but I fail to see why you
vacillate at a time like this

01:29:52.726 --> 01:29:57.665
You would see if I
told you ... but I can't

01:32:40.365 --> 01:32:41.325
Remember this ?

01:32:49.805 --> 01:32:52.125
It's from my factory

01:32:56.845 --> 01:32:58.045
You've saved it ?

01:32:59.245 --> 01:33:00.605
Not just the soap

01:33:02.525 --> 01:33:06.165
Towels, pens, matchboxes
- everything

01:33:10.405 --> 01:33:12.125
Did you ever use it ?

01:33:15.205 --> 01:33:19.685
It's no good for anything,
not even for washing clothes

01:33:25.485 --> 01:33:27.485
What foolish notions I had then

01:33:28.005 --> 01:33:29.245
You still have

01:33:30.885 --> 01:33:35.005
You freed her from her moorings,
now look where she's drifted

01:33:37.593 --> 01:33:39.125
That was no foolish notion

01:33:40.165 --> 01:33:41.365
You still insist ?

01:33:47.045 --> 01:33:51.925
If she likes what she's doing,
then that's the kind of person she is

01:33:53.925 --> 01:33:58.365
I could stop her from going,
but it wouldn't change her

01:34:00.385 --> 01:34:01.885
You can teach a child,
but not the grown-up

01:34:02.566 --> 01:34:04.245
The husband is the master

01:34:06.653 --> 01:34:10.885
Bending her to my will would not help

01:34:12.373 --> 01:34:17.605
At least get him out of the way;
he's not a friendly friend, is he ?

01:34:19.408 --> 01:34:26.565
It would certainly do my estate
good to get him out of the way

01:34:28.393 --> 01:34:32.445
But I'm selfish enough
to think of myself, too

01:34:35.041 --> 01:34:38.525
I can't help it. I must

01:34:39.917 --> 01:34:43.342
If he goes, you'll
find her back by your side

01:34:46.866 --> 01:34:51.205
And I would find her regretting it

01:34:53.199 --> 01:34:56.965
Because she would not be
doing it out of choice

01:34:58.736 --> 01:35:00.005
That would be unbearable

01:35:01.894 --> 01:35:05.885
As much for her as for me

01:35:11.263 --> 01:35:12.943
I can't do it

01:35:13.519 --> 01:35:15.278
Hail Motherland !

01:35:15.359 --> 01:35:17.239
Hail Motherland !

01:35:17.318 --> 01:35:19.199
Hail Motherland !

01:35:19.279 --> 01:35:20.918
Hail Motherland !

01:35:20.999 --> 01:35:22.838
Hail Motherland !

01:35:22.915 --> 01:35:24.562
Hail Motherland !

01:35:24.638 --> 01:35:26.362
Hail Motherland !

01:35:26.438 --> 01:35:28.159
Hail Motherland !

01:35:28.238 --> 01:35:29.839
Hail Motherland !

01:35:32.558 --> 01:35:34.159
Hail Motherland !

01:36:02.260 --> 01:36:03.559
Hail Motherland !

01:36:04.319 --> 01:36:05.399
What is the matter?

01:36:05.959 --> 01:36:06.758
Why so late ?

01:36:07.238 --> 01:36:09.638
That was a lot of work, Mr. Mukherji

01:36:10.718 --> 01:36:12.839
There's a play at Chandrapur tonight;

01:36:12.919 --> 01:36:15.359
I had to wait for the boatmen to go

01:36:15.638 --> 01:36:18.479
These jobs can't be
done with people around

01:36:19.399 --> 01:36:20.558
Mirjan's boat ?

01:36:22.319 --> 01:36:23.039
Good

01:36:24.518 --> 01:36:28.519
But when he comes back and
finds his boat missing ...

01:36:28.598 --> 01:36:33.719
... it won't take him to
put two and two together ...

01:36:34.519 --> 01:36:37.639
... and then he'll come
groveling to you and beg for compensation

01:36:39.278 --> 01:36:43.439
Keep 5,000 or so handy

01:36:46.639 --> 01:36:47.198
I will.

01:36:47.279 --> 01:36:49.679
And now a word of advice ...

01:36:50.999 --> 01:36:54.919
... if you don't mind my being frank

01:36:55.679 --> 01:36:57.719
Out with it. It's late

01:36:58.159 --> 01:37:03.638
I think you should wind
up here fast and decamp

01:37:06.942 --> 01:37:07.718
Why ?

01:37:08.208 --> 01:37:10.039
The outlook's bad

01:37:10.559 --> 01:37:12.158
There may be a riot

01:37:12.991 --> 01:37:14.399
You may be a leader,

01:37:14.756 --> 01:37:19.118
..but you're not exactly
a popular one, you know

01:37:19.723 --> 01:37:24.079
They're certainly not
eager to put you on a pedestal

01:37:27.588 --> 01:37:32.599
I'll decide what to do, Mr.
Sanyal. You don't have to worry

01:37:37.317 --> 01:37:44.724
Onward, sons of India,
the Motherland calls

01:37:44.801 --> 01:37:52.199
Onward, sons of India,
the Motherland calls

01:37:52.276 --> 01:37:59.666
The strong, the brave, the proud,
to serve the nation's cause

01:37:59.800 --> 01:38:07.478
Onward, sons of India,
the Motherland calls

01:38:08.904 --> 01:38:11.119
You should give up
politics and take to singing

01:38:11.852 --> 01:38:16.399
I once had an idea to go on the stage

01:38:17.185 --> 01:38:21.079
It's wonderful to be able to
hold a large audience in your grip

01:38:21.800 --> 01:38:25.799
I thought that when I heard
you speak the other evening

01:38:26.758 --> 01:38:27.998
Of course ...

01:38:28.749 --> 01:38:33.438
... it's nothing like
winning the heart of a woman

01:38:35.078 --> 01:38:38.038
I gather you've won the
hearts of many women ...

01:38:39.078 --> 01:38:42.798
... and not all of them Swadeshi

01:38:43.088 --> 01:38:44.234
This is bad!

01:38:44.840 --> 01:38:46.478
Has Nikhil told you all this ?

01:38:47.851 --> 01:38:51.586
Why not ? After all, you
know such a lot about me

01:38:52.663 --> 01:38:58.358
Youthful indiscretions, that's
what they were - ancient history

01:38:58.853 --> 01:39:01.158
I wonder what happened to those women

01:39:01.929 --> 01:39:06.689
You shouldn't. I'm longer
the same person, you know

01:39:08.049 --> 01:39:10.849
Still, it helps to understand the person

01:39:11.529 --> 01:39:13.649
It's not difficult to understand men

01:39:14.049 --> 01:39:18.889
It's women who are unfathomable;
one despairs of knowing their minds

01:39:19.449 --> 01:39:22.049
You know that song, don't you ?
- What song ?

01:39:23.409 --> 01:39:29.089
"Who can ever fathom a woman's ways ?"

01:39:29.169 --> 01:39:31.969
"Who can ever fathom a woman's ways ?"

01:39:32.529 --> 01:39:35.009
"Her silence mean more than what she says"

01:39:35.809 --> 01:39:38.129
"She looks at you, then drops her eyes"

01:39:38.209 --> 01:39:40.449
"Her silence mean more than what she says"

01:39:40.529 --> 01:39:42.769
"She looks at you, then drops her eyes"

01:39:42.849 --> 01:39:45.409
"She laughs one moment the next she cries"

01:39:46.129 --> 01:39:51.969
"She lingers close,
then leaves you in a daze"

01:39:52.049 --> 01:39:57.729
"Who can ever fathom a woman's ways ?"

01:39:57.809 --> 01:40:00.609
"Who can ever fathom a woman's ways ?"

01:40:01.689 --> 01:40:04.449
Is that why you haven't married ?

01:40:05.729 --> 01:40:10.049
How can I marry if I can't
find a woman after my heart ?

01:40:10.809 --> 01:40:15.329
I waited a long time for you
last night. You didn't come

01:40:18.194 --> 01:40:23.474
Forgive me, Queen. I was
very busy; I got back late

01:40:23.914 --> 01:40:28.274
What were you busy with ?
- The cause of Swadeshi, of course

01:40:28.594 --> 01:40:31.477
Making speeches ?
- Oh, no

01:40:31.554 --> 01:40:32.514
What, then?

01:40:34.074 --> 01:40:39.674
Winding up. I can't stay
here for ever, you know

01:40:41.594 --> 01:40:43.354
We have to be on the move, campaigning

01:40:46.994 --> 01:40:49.554
You'll go away ?

01:40:50.914 --> 01:40:52.674
I must, sooner or later

01:40:55.714 --> 01:40:57.354
What if Queen Bee doesn't let you go ?

01:41:01.714 --> 01:41:04.274
Then no one would be happier than I,

01:41:04.674 --> 01:41:06.834
but I'm not thinking of going yet

01:41:07.314 --> 01:41:09.154
There are problem to be cleared up

01:41:10.674 --> 01:41:11.874
Tell me

01:41:12.594 --> 01:41:13.314
What?

01:41:14.194 --> 01:41:15.594
How much money ?

01:41:25.954 --> 01:41:26.674
Tell me.

01:41:28.069 --> 01:41:32.034
About five thousand, Queen. We
spend more than we reckoned on

01:41:32.395 --> 01:41:36.474
If I get the money, you'll
have to take it without question

01:41:37.692 --> 01:41:41.394
If you say so, but you
mustn't part with your ornaments

01:41:42.442 --> 01:41:44.801
When I said money, I meant money

01:41:47.681 --> 01:41:49.322
What if I can't repay it ?

01:41:50.122 --> 01:41:54.962
I don't expect you to. Can't I
do this much for the cause ?

01:41:57.242 --> 01:41:58.644
I'm worried, Queen

01:41:59.002 --> 01:41:59.642
Why?

01:42:01.802 --> 01:42:06.922
I seem to have become a burden to you.
But I can't help it. I can explain

01:42:07.001 --> 01:42:12.362
You don't have to.
Only tell me one thing

01:42:13.121 --> 01:42:13.922
What?

01:42:15.161 --> 01:42:17.122
If I give you the money, you won't go ?

01:42:17.402 --> 01:42:19.282
Do you think I want to leave you ?

01:42:21.122 --> 01:42:23.482
Then what made you talk of going away ?

01:42:24.161 --> 01:42:30.289
After all the torment I've
been through, only for your sake

01:42:30.598 --> 01:42:31.217
And..

01:42:31.294 --> 01:42:32.027
And you?

01:43:25.361 --> 01:43:29.762
The Hindus ask you to
join hands with them

01:43:30.761 --> 01:43:34.802
They wheedle you, they coax you...

01:43:35.247 --> 01:43:38.722
... they even use threats

01:43:38.801 --> 01:43:42.962
They want you to take
up Swadeshi at all costs

01:43:43.540 --> 01:43:47.681
Don't let their words misguide you

01:43:48.456 --> 01:43:53.801
Hindus don't care for your well-being

01:43:54.032 --> 01:43:57.122
They don't care about you at all.

01:43:57.796 --> 01:44:04.361
Their one aim is to keep you
under their heels for ever

01:44:05.892 --> 01:44:08.932
Don't forget that in Bengal...

01:44:09.172 --> 01:44:15.252
... Muslims are in the majority,
Muslims are mostly peasants

01:44:16.292 --> 01:44:18.372
The country's wealth...

01:44:18.452 --> 01:44:21.772
...comes from the land

01:44:22.692 --> 01:44:26.572
No part of this wealth
is produced by the Hindus

01:44:27.372 --> 01:44:31.252
It's you who enriched them

01:44:31.692 --> 01:44:36.332
They have no right to
the fruit of your labour

01:44:36.652 --> 01:44:41.572
They use their cunning to
appropriate what you sweat to produce

01:44:42.812 --> 01:44:45.292
So, brother Muslims...

01:44:45.810 --> 01:44:51.092
...do not listen to the Hindus,
don't get mixed up in their politics

01:44:51.492 --> 01:44:53.492
Swadeshi is not for you

01:44:55.292 --> 01:44:59.172
I've sent for you because you lead
the Hindu community in this village

01:45:00.532 --> 01:45:04.332
You are men of discretion and judgement

01:45:05.772 --> 01:45:12.372
I think you will appreciate
what I am going to tell you

01:45:13.530 --> 01:45:14.892
I trust you will

01:45:15.972 --> 01:45:17.492
I only want to say...

01:45:19.292 --> 01:45:21.652
...while we can hold on to
our own religious beliefs...

01:45:23.092 --> 01:45:24.932
... we cannot interfere
with the belief of others

01:45:26.932 --> 01:45:28.172
Even amongst us Hindus...

01:45:29.852 --> 01:45:32.292
...a Vaishnava has no right to prevent
a Shakta spilling the blood of animals

01:45:33.892 --> 01:45:37.332
So, in order to live by their
own religious convictions...

01:45:38.692 --> 01:45:41.212
... the Muslims must be left free

01:45:41.852 --> 01:45:45.252
The Muslims in this
village never slaughtered cows

01:45:45.332 --> 01:45:49.092
We hear they're now doing so

01:45:51.652 --> 01:45:53.092
I've heard so, too

01:45:54.879 --> 01:45:58.772
But I strongly believe that
they're being forced to do so...

01:45:59.760 --> 01:46:04.772
...to stir up trouble
between the two sects

01:46:07.349 --> 01:46:09.252
I urge you not to add fuel to the fire

01:46:09.754 --> 01:46:12.434
They won't stop unless
you put them down, sir.

01:46:12.754 --> 01:46:14.674
The good old days are gone

01:46:15.792 --> 01:46:20.234
Listen. Muslims are a part of India

01:46:21.754 --> 01:46:28.314
This is a fact of history.
You must accept the fact

01:46:30.674 --> 01:46:34.914
We can't imagine an
India without Muslims

01:46:36.754 --> 01:46:40.714
If we try to put them down, it'll
not only not stop the killing of cows

01:46:42.434 --> 01:46:44.754
It may lead to the killing of men

01:46:47.847 --> 01:46:53.034
Never more so than in
the present state of unrest

01:46:54.961 --> 01:47:00.674
You have a grave responsibility now

01:47:05.233 --> 01:47:08.914
I beseech you, I pray you

01:47:11.213 --> 01:47:13.754
Do not encourage hatred

01:47:15.394 --> 01:47:19.994
To do so now would be to court disaster

01:47:35.274 --> 01:47:36.594
Hail Motherland !

01:47:37.994 --> 01:47:39.594
Hail Motherland !

01:48:13.289 --> 01:48:14.034
Nikhil.

01:48:15.065 --> 01:48:16.314
Did you hear a shot ?

01:48:16.848 --> 01:48:17.568
I did.

01:48:18.088 --> 01:48:19.868
What now ?

01:48:19.945 --> 01:48:24.208
I know what must be done

01:48:24.849 --> 01:48:25.968
But first,

01:48:26.448 --> 01:48:29.649
...take my carriage, go home and
come back with your belongings

01:48:30.568 --> 01:48:33.408
The roads are no longer safe; I
don't want you to get into trouble

01:48:34.329 --> 01:48:36.208
That's all very well, but...

01:48:37.768 --> 01:48:39.528
I'll tell Sandip right away

01:49:09.528 --> 01:49:12.849
Time's running out; I
must have the money now

01:49:21.098 --> 01:49:23.658
What's that ?
- Can't you guess ?

01:49:25.498 --> 01:49:26.338
Money ?

01:49:27.415 --> 01:49:28.738
Hardly enough.

01:49:29.058 --> 01:49:30.538
There can't be more
than 500 in those bags

01:49:31.458 --> 01:49:34.378
You must have forgotten,
I asked for 5,000

01:49:40.178 --> 01:49:40.858
What is this?

01:49:42.978 --> 01:49:43.938
Gold coins?

01:49:53.018 --> 01:49:54.258
Gold !

01:49:56.578 --> 01:49:58.258
Gold!

01:50:02.058 --> 01:50:06.778
You should have told me,
or how else would I know ?

01:50:09.498 --> 01:50:10.938
Please don't be angry, Queen

01:50:11.858 --> 01:50:12.578
Sandip.

01:50:18.138 --> 01:50:20.618
I've come to talk to you
- What about?

01:50:22.058 --> 01:50:23.858
I don't want you to stay any longer

01:50:24.698 --> 01:50:29.178
Things have taken a serious turn;
your presence may make matters worse

01:50:30.418 --> 01:50:32.578
I want you to leave
Suksayar by tomorrow morning

01:50:34.618 --> 01:50:36.859
Am I supposed to take orders from you ?

01:50:37.290 --> 01:50:38.818
It's not that

01:50:40.178 --> 01:50:45.098
Your leaving for Calcutta will
help you and ease the situation here

01:50:46.378 --> 01:50:48.178
I have nothing to do in Calcutta

01:50:48.258 --> 01:50:49.818
All the more reason to go

01:50:50.657 --> 01:50:52.460
You've done too much here

01:50:54.860 --> 01:50:56.900
Don't think I haven't been informed

01:50:58.380 --> 01:51:01.300
From setting fire to
the peasants' barns...

01:51:02.180 --> 01:51:03.740
... to sinking Mirjan's boat

01:51:05.740 --> 01:51:11.980
You speak of Hindu-Moslem unity,
but in fact you oppress Muslims

01:51:13.500 --> 01:51:15.100
I shan't put up with it any longer

01:51:17.860 --> 01:51:19.660
I may not believe in Swadeshi...

01:51:21.140 --> 01:51:23.300
...but I have true
admiration for some Swadeshi leaders

01:51:24.820 --> 01:51:29.380
But not for those whose
actions believe their words

01:51:31.180 --> 01:51:33.220
You're harming the country,
not saving it.

01:51:34.860 --> 01:51:36.860
This mustn't go on in my estate

01:51:37.780 --> 01:51:40.540
There's only one person
here I'm prepared to listen to

01:51:43.500 --> 01:51:48.300
Queen, do you want me to stay or go ?

01:51:57.343 --> 01:51:58.100
Queen.

01:51:59.690 --> 01:52:01.620
I'm waiting for your answer

01:52:03.534 --> 01:52:05.580
Do you want that I
should leave Suksayar ?

01:52:08.860 --> 01:52:09.940
Tell me, Queen

01:52:12.260 --> 01:52:13.580
I've said what I came to say

01:52:16.540 --> 01:52:17.900
I hope I won't have to repeat it

01:52:23.220 --> 01:52:24.140
Queen.

01:52:27.060 --> 01:52:28.340
What's the matter with you ?

01:52:32.694 --> 01:52:33.620
All of a sudden..

01:52:33.697 --> 01:52:35.100
Is Amulya in your room ?

01:52:35.700 --> 01:52:36.860
Amulya? - Yes.

01:52:37.530 --> 01:52:38.540
Why ?

01:52:38.620 --> 01:52:40.700
Ask him to see me. It's urgent

01:52:42.100 --> 01:52:43.980
Can't you tell me the reason ?

01:52:44.980 --> 01:52:50.300
No, I'll tell Amulya.
Please send him to me

01:52:52.060 --> 01:52:53.020
Very well

01:54:26.395 --> 01:54:27.075
Amulya.

01:54:30.115 --> 01:54:32.995
Can you do me a favour ?
- Certainly

01:54:33.275 --> 01:54:36.995
Take the morning train to
Calcutta and return in the evening

01:54:37.395 --> 01:54:39.315
Money for the journey is in this box

01:54:39.515 --> 01:54:40.715
What box is that ?

01:54:41.195 --> 01:54:46.075
My jewel case. I need 5,000 rupees.
Sell some of my ornaments

01:54:46.155 --> 01:54:48.195
I'll get you the money without that

01:54:48.275 --> 01:54:52.475
How ? It's not a small sum

01:54:52.555 --> 01:54:53.715
I'll get it

01:54:54.035 --> 01:54:56.115
No, do as I tell you

01:54:56.635 --> 01:54:59.475
But why did you give Mr.
Mukherji 5,000 rupees ?

01:54:59.555 --> 01:55:01.435
He said he needed 5,000

01:55:01.515 --> 01:55:04.715
No, we worked out that we needed 3,500.

01:55:05.075 --> 01:55:07.595
If he gets more, he spends it on himself

01:55:08.155 --> 01:55:11.235
He's quite a spender; he
always by travels first-class

01:55:12.915 --> 01:55:13.798
Mr. Mukherji ?

01:55:13.875 --> 01:55:14.555
Yes, sister.

01:55:14.915 --> 01:55:18.235
He says hardship
saps a leader's strength

01:55:19.512 --> 01:55:22.395
Well, I shan't take back
what I've already given

01:55:22.730 --> 01:55:25.595
It may be needed later.
You get me the 5,000.

01:55:26.010 --> 01:55:29.115
Put the box away. I'll
get you the money tonight

01:55:29.342 --> 01:55:31.315
How ?
- From the treasury

01:55:32.122 --> 01:55:35.235
Are you mad ? What about the guards ?

01:55:35.393 --> 01:55:37.155
But we carry arms

01:55:44.936 --> 01:55:46.736
Good heavens !

01:55:47.736 --> 01:55:51.856
Working for the country requires funds

01:55:52.936 --> 01:55:54.936
Have you no qualms about robbing ?

01:55:55.016 --> 01:55:59.456
Whose money is it ? Mine today,
the moneylender's tomorrow

01:55:59.830 --> 01:56:02.416
Why not use it for the cause ?

01:56:02.616 --> 01:56:07.256
No, Amulya. If you go robbing
treasuries, I'll die of fear

01:56:07.576 --> 01:56:09.496
Do as I tell you

01:56:09.656 --> 01:56:15.616
Sell as much as you need
to and bring back the rest

01:56:16.496 --> 01:56:19.896
And be careful, for heaven's sake

01:56:21.336 --> 01:56:22.216
Very well

01:56:26.456 --> 01:56:27.096
I am leaving.

01:56:27.416 --> 01:56:28.136
Yes.

01:56:51.776 --> 01:56:52.536
Queen.

01:57:02.767 --> 01:57:03.776
You're going ?

01:57:04.455 --> 01:57:06.456
Is there any reason for me to stay ?

01:57:06.750 --> 01:57:07.776
Why do you say that ?

01:57:08.791 --> 01:57:10.936
Can't you hear the not of discord ?

01:57:12.336 --> 01:57:16.696
If I've done anything wrong,
please forgive me. Don't go like this

01:57:18.096 --> 01:57:21.856
My husband says the less one
knows you, the better one like you

01:57:23.256 --> 01:57:25.336
Perhaps I know you too well

01:57:25.904 --> 01:57:30.056
Don't say that. Has
knowing me meant nothing to you ?

01:57:31.006 --> 01:57:32.046
Has it all been in vain ?

01:57:32.965 --> 01:57:35.326
I believed you'd succeed,

01:57:36.085 --> 01:57:37.405
I wanted you to succeed
in what you were doing

01:57:38.046 --> 01:57:39.325
But not any more ?

01:57:42.046 --> 01:57:42.685
No.

01:58:05.125 --> 01:58:09.369
Allah is great !

01:58:09.445 --> 01:58:11.605
Allah is great !

01:58:11.686 --> 01:58:13.446
Allah is great !

01:58:13.525 --> 01:58:15.286
Allah is great !

01:58:17.046 --> 01:58:19.326
Allah is great !

01:58:19.846 --> 01:58:21.486
Allah is great !

01:58:21.606 --> 01:58:23.806
Allah is great !

01:58:59.566 --> 01:59:00.286
Who is it?

01:59:00.726 --> 01:59:01.566
Who is it?

01:59:03.126 --> 01:59:04.086
Who is it? Who is it?

01:59:08.206 --> 01:59:09.046
Hands up !

01:59:12.242 --> 01:59:13.045
Hands up.

01:59:15.966 --> 01:59:18.246
Go indoors !

01:59:24.676 --> 01:59:25.525
Come on.

01:59:28.185 --> 01:59:29.086
Turn round !

01:59:30.295 --> 01:59:31.045
Turn around.

01:59:35.672 --> 01:59:37.112
Now open the safe

01:59:38.232 --> 01:59:38.871
Come on.

01:59:44.472 --> 01:59:47.432
Open it and count out 3,500 rupees

01:59:48.235 --> 01:59:51.591
What's going on ?

01:59:51.672 --> 01:59:52.992
What's the hue and cry about ?

01:59:54.912 --> 01:59:58.551
I don't know. I hope it's not a riot

01:59:58.823 --> 02:00:00.192
What are you saying, brother-in-law?

02:00:01.112 --> 02:00:03.752
What will happen to us ?

02:00:05.631 --> 02:00:09.872
We're going to Calcutta
tomorrow; it's no longer safe here

02:00:10.272 --> 02:00:13.032
Who is "we" ? Aren't I coming with you ?

02:00:15.591 --> 02:00:16.592
Did I say that ?

02:00:19.431 --> 02:00:23.352
The Chakravarty's
treasury has been raided

02:00:23.432 --> 02:00:25.712
What's to stop them raiding this place ?

02:00:26.352 --> 02:00:29.832
If they kill me they'll burn my
body by the shriveled banyan.

02:00:29.912 --> 02:00:31.112
That's awful

02:00:33.272 --> 02:00:36.992
Start packing; and don't
forget your Talking Machine

02:00:38.493 --> 02:00:40.112
You're not joking, are you ?

02:00:41.220 --> 02:00:45.512
Am I the frivolous
type ? Don't you know me ?

02:01:09.307 --> 02:01:10.112
Bimala.

02:01:13.678 --> 02:01:15.118
I want to tell you something

02:01:15.559 --> 02:01:16.159
What?

02:01:17.438 --> 02:01:21.199
There were 5,000 rupees in
gold coins in two bags in the safe

02:01:22.078 --> 02:01:24.038
I gave them to Sandip

02:01:24.398 --> 02:01:25.639
He needed the money

02:01:26.998 --> 02:01:30.718
Now you know how
hard it is to refuse him

02:01:30.878 --> 02:01:32.359
I'll replace it

02:01:32.678 --> 02:01:36.319
I've given my jewel case to Amulya;
he'll sell ornaments to get the money

02:01:42.038 --> 02:01:46.598
I felt bad speaking to
Sandip like that in your presence

02:01:49.438 --> 02:01:53.798
But I had to. Things
have taken a bad turn

02:01:58.558 --> 02:02:00.638
It's no longer safe for him here

02:02:02.198 --> 02:02:03.878
What about you ?

02:02:08.198 --> 02:02:14.278
Your safety is what
concerns me; no one else's matters

02:02:15.439 --> 02:02:20.198
Tomorrow we're going to Calcutta.
All three of us

02:02:21.679 --> 02:02:23.518
And if something happens before then ?

02:02:27.038 --> 02:02:28.598
You won't leave the house, will you ?

02:02:31.478 --> 02:02:35.078
If something should happen I'd
have to go and intervene, Bimala

02:02:39.518 --> 02:02:40.639
I knew

02:02:43.147 --> 02:02:45.878
I knew I'd be punished

02:02:52.759 --> 02:02:57.158
Punished ? Why ? You
have not done anything wrong

02:02:59.294 --> 02:03:03.575
I can't even ask for forgiveness

02:03:06.134 --> 02:03:11.623
But you've come back
to me, haven't you ?

02:03:20.901 --> 02:03:24.854
What an age it seems since I
last looked at you and spoke to you

02:03:27.215 --> 02:03:31.615
What came over me ? Why
do such things happen ?

02:03:34.175 --> 02:03:35.815
You've done nothing wrong, Bimala

02:03:36.734 --> 02:03:39.295
For ten years you
didn't look at another man

02:03:41.855 --> 02:03:43.454
Why do you forget that ?

02:04:14.485 --> 02:04:15.845
There's 3,500 rupees here

02:04:17.485 --> 02:04:20.085
Please return the jewel
case and the gold coins

02:04:21.862 --> 02:04:24.645
Where did you get the
money ? Where have you been ?

02:04:25.885 --> 02:04:27.365
To the sub-treasury at Chakna

02:04:28.888 --> 02:04:30.285
I hope nobody saw you

02:04:37.965 --> 02:04:39.085
I covered my face

02:04:40.045 --> 02:04:42.685
Did you see any trouble ?
- There's a riot

02:04:44.925 --> 02:04:47.565
Muslims have broken into
the temple of Visalakshi

02:04:58.005 --> 02:04:59.165
You're going ?

02:05:01.205 --> 02:05:02.805
Yes. To Rongpur

02:05:07.965 --> 02:05:09.165
Will you come with me ?

02:05:22.285 --> 02:05:23.205
I must go now

02:05:31.565 --> 02:05:32.605
Hail Motherland !

02:05:34.045 --> 02:05:35.405
Hail Motherland !

02:05:49.005 --> 02:05:50.005
What are you thinking ?

02:05:51.605 --> 02:05:52.605
Nothing

02:05:54.885 --> 02:05:56.725
I don't want to think

02:05:58.445 --> 02:05:59.925
I want to forget

02:06:01.885 --> 02:06:04.725
All that has happened
in the last few days

02:06:05.405 --> 02:06:07.885
Why must you forget ?

02:06:12.485 --> 02:06:13.525
Come in, Sandip

02:06:17.221 --> 02:06:19.062
This is the age of breaking rules.

02:06:20.101 --> 02:06:21.501
Your wife came out of seclusion...

02:06:22.302 --> 02:06:25.621
...and now I've invaded
the privacy of your bedroom

02:06:28.422 --> 02:06:32.064
These are your property,
which I duly return

02:06:33.102 --> 02:06:35.982
One jewel case and
two bags of gold coins

02:06:36.822 --> 02:06:37.422
Jewel case ?

02:06:38.982 --> 02:06:42.621
Your devotee didn't take it with him,
but he's brought the money

02:06:45.861 --> 02:06:47.742
Since you have your valuables,

02:06:47.821 --> 02:06:50.101
I hope you won't mind
my keeping the money

02:06:50.701 --> 02:06:51.702
Are you going ?

02:06:52.182 --> 02:06:56.142
Yes, Nikhil. The train to
Rongpur leaves in an hour

02:06:58.464 --> 02:07:02.862
You can hear the sound of
riot; Amulya witnessed it

02:07:03.661 --> 02:07:07.581
So I must make my proverbial escape;

02:07:08.382 --> 02:07:12.102
I must live to finish my work, you know

02:07:12.781 --> 02:07:14.502
Don't make the same mistake again.

02:07:15.301 --> 02:07:16.821
Can't you see the result of your action

02:07:18.462 --> 02:07:20.181
I follow the Gita, Nikhil

02:07:20.821 --> 02:07:24.222
I am concerned only with the action,
not with the result

02:07:24.702 --> 02:07:28.182
And I consider Ravana to be
the hero of Ramayana, not Rama

02:07:28.941 --> 02:07:31.902
So I can't listen to
the followers of Rama

02:07:32.781 --> 02:07:34.821
The straight path is not my path

02:07:36.301 --> 02:07:37.821
Well, it's time to say good-bye

02:07:43.062 --> 02:07:45.102
I'm keeping this as a memento

02:07:50.181 --> 02:07:54.901
Who knows if we'll ever meet again ?

02:07:57.942 --> 02:07:58.941
Good-bye, Nikhil

02:08:03.741 --> 02:08:04.701
Queen Bee

02:08:10.981 --> 02:08:12.702
Hail Motherland !

02:08:47.403 --> 02:08:52.141
Courage, Bimala. I
must go out to them now

02:08:54.024 --> 02:08:55.741
I must

02:08:58.024 --> 02:09:02.221
Don't stop me. Please

02:09:32.655 --> 02:09:33.649
You let him go ?

02:09:33.726 --> 02:09:36.410
He wouldn't heed us

02:09:38.441 --> 02:09:44.060
You witch ! You send him to his death !

02:09:45.181 --> 02:09:48.942
Have you no pity in
your heart of stone ?

